Package org.eclipse.mat.collect

Class HashMapObjectLong<E>

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mat.collect.HashMapObjectLong<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class HashMapObjectLong<E> extends Object implements Serializable
A map from Object to long. More efficient than a general map null not allowed as key.
